x10.constraint.xnative
Class XNativeLit

java.lang.Object
  x10.constraint.xnative.XNativeTerm
      x10.constraint.xnative.XNativeVar
          x10.constraint.xnative.XNativeLit
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, XLit, XTerm, XVar
public class XNativeLit
extends XNativeVar
implements XLit

A representation of a literal. A literal is an XVar carrying a payload that is equal to any other XLit carrying the same payload. This class and its subclasses should not have mutable state.

Author:
vijay
